create or replace view smoke_test_db.view_from_multiple_tables
            as 
            (
                select a.date_utc, a.revenue, b.revenue as revenue2, c.revenue as revenue3 
                from 
                    smoke_test_db.base_table a
                left join 
                    smoke_test_db.lineage_from_base b 
                    on a.date_utc = b.date_utc 
                left join 
                    smoke_test_db_2.table_from_other_db c 
                    on b.date_utc = c.date_utc 
            );
